\begin_layout Section*
Criticisms, factors of success
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In this short survey of EA DICE internal service structure, we have found
 few to points to criticise.
 The structures seem few, sparsely documented, of an ad-hoc nature, and
 are reported to work well.
 The main challenges are reported to be communication of ideas.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
It is unlikely the technical success is owed to meticulous design of procedures
 and structures.
 We look for factors of success elsewhere.
\end_layout

