\begin_layout Subsection*
Conclusions: leadership
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
DICE provides an example of how effectively internal services can work,
 but provides little guidance on how to emulate it in terms of structures,
 procedures, and operations.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The key factors at play are likely to be leadership, which merits further
 study.
\end_layout

